                </h6>
                <textarea id="victory" name="victory">Thought about and recorded what I wanted to accomplish, reasons for accomplishing it, and how to do it.</textarea>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field blue-arrow">
                <select id="status" name="status">
                    <option value="Private" selected>Private</option>
                    <option value="Public">Public</option>
                </select>
                <label for="status">
                    Status &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    <span class="guidance">(Keep goal creation private or open for others to see)</span>
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <input type="submit" value="Save" class="btn">
